    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Term first used by Sheraton to describe armchairs having a semicircular back and elongated seat, the shape suggesting an open carriage.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
